<span style="font-size: x-small;">Oberle, E. et. Al. (2016) Stress contagion in the classroom? The link between classroom teacher burnout and morning cortisol in elementary school students. <i>Social Science &amp; Medicine</i>; 159: 30-37.&nbsp;</span></div>
